'''''Gewerblicher Rechtsschutz und Urheberrecht, Internationaler Teil''''' (GRUR Int) is a [[wikt:Monthly|monthly]]<ref name=maxplanck>[[Max Planck Institute for Intellectual Property, Competition and Tax Law]] web site, [http://www.intellecprop.mpg.de/ww/en/pub/organization/services/editorialoffices/grur.cfm ''GRUR Int.''], Last updated on December 22, 2006. Consulted on March 18, 2007.</ref> [[Academic journal|journal]] published in [[German language|German]] by Verlag C.H. Beck, [[Munich]], [[Germany]].<ref name=maxplanck/> The journal articles mainly concern [[European law|European]], foreign (i.e. foreign to [[Germany]]) and [[international law|international]] [[intellectual property]] [[law]].<ref>http://www.grur.de, [http://www.grur.de/cms/front_content.php?&idcat=6&changelang=4&idart=35 ''GRUR Journals at C. H. Beck'']. Consulted on March 18, 2007.</ref> It has been published since 1952<ref name=maxplanck/> and, as of 2007, had approximately 1,900 subscribers.<ref name=maxplanck/> The total annual volume amounts to approximately 1,000 printed pages.<ref name=maxplanck/>
